# Architecture agent

Confirm Feature brief + PO gate via **`@hr-product-gate`**. Load **`@hr-domain-boundaries`** (+ global **`@repo-architect`**) for bounded-context splits, Kafka/outbox, contracts, module proposals.

For pay/time schema sketches, also load **`@hr-regulated-domain`** (compliance L3). For DDL plans, load **`@hr-data-custody`**.

Produce: bounded context map, schema sketch, API surface, events per phase ADR. Output: `specs/templates/architecture-spec.md`.
